//To convert all characters to lower/upper case 
transform(name1.begin(), name1.end(), name1.begin(), ::tolower);
transform(name2.begin(), name2.end(), name2.begin(), ::toupper);

//Comparing two strings
string1.compare(string2)
It returns a negative value if string1 is less than second string, returns 0 when the two strings are equal
and returns value greater than 0 if the first string is greater than the second

//To find the absolute value of the given number 
abs(number)
eg:- abs(-5) = 5


